                            <lb ed="I" n="0031a03"/>禪寺
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031a04"/>碑記
                    </div2>
                    <div2>
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b01"/>□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b02"/><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">神</unclear>□□□□□□□<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">不</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">夜</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">者</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">也</unclear>□□□□<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">垂</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">慈</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">暉</unclear>□□□□□<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">之</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">上</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">久</unclear>□□□□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b03"/>化於億載□□<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">之</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">下</unclear>。大千燭<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">茲</unclear>昏□<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">且</unclear>隱顯弗瓻揖G。□□□□□□□□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b04"/>非運資廣因。樹應曩世。豈能開扇道風。施沾法雨者哉。<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">仰</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">惟</unclear>
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b05"/>皇帝陛下。纂統重光。紹隆累聖。德洽三才。道均五緯。政極<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">辰</unclear>□。□□□□<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">乃</unclear>□□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b06"/>源。遊神法菀。慧鼓既振。普天聞般若之音。頹綱更開。率土悟火宅<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">之</unclear>□□□□□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b07"/>場斯趣矣。自惟<note n="0031001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30318;＝&CB30397;【中研院】</note><app n="0031001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">&CB30397;</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30318;</rdg></app>蹤。冀方樹基。勃海并世。□宛著姓。神州靈降。盛□□□□□□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b08"/>淂戚聯。朝旭昵親<unclear cert="above_medium" reason="damage">夕</unclear><note n="0031002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB06418;＝容【中研院】</note><app n="0031002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">容</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB06418;</rdg></app>。內秉望舒之讚。外憖阿衡之翼。入<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">總</unclear>謀<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">議</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">出</unclear>□□□□□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b09"/>沖波坤津潛液寒。族貫春日之榮幽。附沾夏辰之蔚輝。<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">顯</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">哉</unclear>□<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">而</unclear>□□□□□□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b10"/>渥而溳心罔謝。遂仰慕皇緯報施之功。亦尋聖經緣果之旨。□詳<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">群</unclear>□□□□□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b11"/>蘭厥靈岑。擇茲&CB00583;嶺。上涌沖天之峰。下帶□岫之險。重<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">基</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">雲</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">構</unclear>。<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">飛</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">級</unclear>□□□□□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b12"/><note n="0031003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30409;＝槃【中研院】</note><app n="0031003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">槃</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30409;</rdg></app>屈虯電暐豔琨成。瑍若資神。乃□□質沉。堅翠□外。□<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">麗</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">炎</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">新</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">至</unclear>□<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">之</unclear>□□□<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">在</unclear>
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b13"/><note n="0031004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB05471;＝希【中研院】</note><app n="0031004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">希</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB05471;</rdg></app>世之相。千像吐琦。万形挺妙。苕苕焉。暉赫萃乎<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">兆</unclear>日。<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">修</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">修</unclear>焉。<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">感</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">發</unclear>□□□□□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b14"/>斯誠。冀微功鍾於至德。顯福應於道祚。述遵休風。遂興<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">頌</unclear>曰。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b15"/>修哉渾源。冥化琨成。道氣既開。□像垂形。紛華競耀。至猷<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">淹</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">經</unclear>。<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">聖</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">覺</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">匪</unclear>□。□□□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b16"/><note n="0031005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30410;＝恢【中研院】</note><app n="0031005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">恢</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30410;</rdg></app><note n="0031006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30410;＝恢【中研院】</note><app n="0031006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">恢</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30410;</rdg></app>至謨。苕苕遐宣。道流三界。化溢大千。幽衢<note n="0031007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30318;＝&CB30397;【中研院】</note><app n="0031007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">&CB30397;</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30318;</rdg></app>轍。靜<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">境</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">亟</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">埏</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">隱</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">顯</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">弗</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage"></unclear>□□□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b17"/>聖皇沖感。靈液遐融。潤均法海。扇協道風。悟因訓<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">萃</unclear>。果隨<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">業</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">崇</unclear>。□<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">區</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">萇</unclear>□□□□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b18"/>靈降聖德。二后經綸。內光椒掖。外允九臣。齊思渭陽。嘉爵交<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">臻</unclear>。誓被□□□□□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b19"/>沉<note n="0031008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00116;＝谿【中研院】</note><app n="0031008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">谿</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00116;</rdg></app><unclear cert="above_medium" reason="damage">賁</unclear>壑。峰山霄星。風雲交液。吐化蚕類。玄堂暐豔。聖容<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">啟</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">靈</unclear>。<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">樹</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">銘</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">興</unclear>□□□□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0031b20"/><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">大</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">魏</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">永</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">平</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">二</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">年</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">歲</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">在</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">己</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">丑</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">四</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">月</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">戊</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">申</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">朔</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">八</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">日</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">乙</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">卯</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">使</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">持</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">節</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">都</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">督</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">涇</unclear>□□□□□
                    </div2>
